# Voice Shiritori

Voice Shiritori is a Python game of shiritori using voice commands and custom dictonary maker.

## Installation

Download the database file:http://compling.hss.ntu.edu.sg/wnja/
Use the dictonary maker python to make your own shiritori dictionary


## Usage

Start the main program and follow the instructions on screen, be sure to have your microphone ready.

## Contributing
Pull requests are welcome. For major changes, please open an issue first to discuss what you would like to change.
